#- Delivero has returned. We were a courier company that operated server wide from September 2013 to January 2014. Talks on bringing back the company began between myself and former courier Defmork in late November - knowing the Nether was not


#- too far off and wanting to take a short break from the game I decided to delay the announcement until January.

Delivero is officially named §o"Royal Delivero"§r and is under the care of the Courier Guild Grandmaster of Epicus 
#- to be myself. The brand name itself is
owned by TheJDz and all Delivero property is under his control. These changes in ownership were brought about over the summer. TheJDz is a really cool guy - I've always enjoyed working him.



#- Delivero now operates exclusively with official partners. We ship materials in bulk free of charge to the customer and instead take a small cut of the producer's profit. We make sure that prices are not adjusted to cover courier fees. This means Delivero


#- is not available for hire by the general public, at least for the month of January. Should you wish to partner with Delivero - please contact me on reddit and we can work towards including you in our February list of partners if possible.



#- Public Delivero Partners (free delivery server wide from these producers):

