------------------

#- I understand that this is a very differently operated Delivero than you may have been familiar with. With nether travel we expect to be far less busy. Limiting ourselves to official partners ensures quality of service and prevents burn out.



#- Many thanks to Defmork for contacting me on my break and convincing me to kickstart the 'auld courier wagon once again.

Lord_Pericorp

Delivero




